{"tid":1106976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国《新編學生字典》「有自慰沒自由」　","createTime":"2019-04-15T02:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T06:56:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c80ea99c6810fdce6f7cfb4ca0151d5e6f9eaa36","tid":1106976,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/4-11/p2401111a873338828-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F4-11%2Fp2401111a873338828-ss.jpg&h=a0c7ea6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有民眾發現中國人民教育出版社的《新編學生字典》中，在生字「自」的介紹中，出現「自慰」等詞彙，卻沒有「自由」一詞，引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n日前，有網友在社交平台臉書上表示，中國人民教育出版社的《新編學生字典》中，學生如果查找「自」的意思，會看到字典中有「自卑」、「自慰」、「自豪」、「自謙」、「自信」、「自願」、「自重」、「自尊」、「自得其樂」、「自欺欺人」、「自取滅亡」、「自作聰明」等詞彙。<br />\n<br />\n網友對此表示質疑為什麼沒有「自由」一詞，並吐槽說，「有自慰沒自由」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，有外媒報導稱，這家出版社在2013年時，旗下出版的《新華字典》同樣刪去了「自由」一詞，不過，在2004年版、2010年版中，還能查到「自由」詞彙，當時著名學者傅國湧用字典裡的詞彙諷刺道：「雖沒了自由，但多了自慰，自得其樂，自欺欺人，自取滅亡」。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，不少網友們批評中共治下的大陸政府在「洗腦教育」民眾，「自慰都敢提，不敢提自由」、「有自慰沒自由, 非常符合共產黨現狀。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/04/11/890207.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F890207.html&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvXHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=bbc114a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/04/11/890207.html</a>"},{"pid":"e071c043ad0e0108fc7ac90ae6491242ab01a6b1","tid":1106976,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a613b19dcd9390b750b21aa89ea1560f63fc72","tid":1106976,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a930b57d8276b4f11f975b8b82781af9b64504b6","tid":1106976,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1521894ff7c6285ddac650eafc2aae8b4c8959b0","tid":1106976,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"當熊貓都冇自由嘅時候，你有得自慰咪算好囉"},{"pid":"c71dd38f5533368fd10f1fcaa85b517c4a637df3","tid":1106976,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"1984<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}